     H            Y.                                                      FEAR03
     F** AJFR08 ************************************
     F* ..  PICK UP WAITING TIME OF SCREEN DDSA SPECIFICATION..*
     F* I-HASADA                     91.10.28      *
     F************************************ AJFR08 **
     FSRCFILE IF  F      92            DISK
     ISRCFILE AA  01
     I                                       18  18 SYO
     I                                       19  20 CMT
     I                                       29  29 CMT1
     I                                       57  62 KWRD
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           WAIT    6
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WAIT
      *
     C           STEP01    TAG
     C                     READ SRCFILE                  02
     C           *IN02     CABEQ'1'       STEP02
     C           CMT       CABEQ'A*'      STEP01
     C           CMT1      CABEQ'R'       STEP02
     C           KWRD      CABNE'INVITE'  STEP01
     C                     Z-ADD180       JKAN    60
     C                     MOVE JKAN      WAIT
     C                     GOTO END
      *
     C           STEP02    TAG
     C                     MOVE '*NOMAX'  WAIT
     C           END       TAG
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
